{
  "stem": "17001.8",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 28.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then some of the potato that would smash on the cement, the other girls licked it up, and they had a picnic out of it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But if any of the German [GERMAN] had noticed that I lift up my arm and I'm throwing the potatoes, I would get such a beating I would be right there.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "One day, there were this girl who I befriended.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because to tell you the honest truth, I figured it out that eventually we going to be liberated.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we didn't know if it's going to be the Russians or the English or who.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I was trying to be selfish, and I was trying to befriend girls who spoke different languages.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I figured, this way I will able to communicate to-- to-- to be alive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I felt so stupid that I didn't know German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I-- I really-- maybe that was my luck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So what happened is that I befriended this girl.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was also from around the upper part of the mountains.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was a beautiful person.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A very, very lovely looking, very nice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was a rabbi's daughter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One morning, she came to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She said, Magda.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I dreamt with my father, which I never did before.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was complaining and I was crying that we can't take this anymore.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's too much.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So my father puts his hand on my head and says, my dear daughter-- you know, in Yiddish-- be patient.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When you eat an apple, you start at the skin, and then you get to the core.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So you will get there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was in the morning that she told me this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were taking them out to the forest somewhere.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "To do what, don't ask me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They brought her back dead.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
